description:
&lt;p&gt;Thames Medical District Nursing team are looking for dynamic, enthusiastic, hardworking and highly motivated nurses to join are award winning and extremely friendly team based in Weybridge.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post would suit newly qualified or experienced community nurses looking for full or part time roles. Excellent training will be provided and you will work alongside district nurses and team leaders who will ensure you have the necessary support for your ongoing personal development. You will be provided with a robust induction and regular 1:1&#39;s. Opportunities to further your community career by undertaking the District Nurse specialist qualification are available.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The District Nursing team visits patients within their own homes, residential care homes and clinic settings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It is a 7 day a week service between the hours of 9-5pm therefore you will be expected to work weekends. &lt;strong&gt;A car driver is essential.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
